      "Missing 0x000001 prefix at offset 0 indicates non-MPEG or corrupted file",
      "Non-monotonic SCR values across pack headers indicate stream splicing or corruption",
      "Extremely large PES packet sizes may indicate buffer overflow attempt in legacy players"
